description:
At this time of year, many unbiblical understandings about life after death are being promoted. Pastor Ted Wilson, president of the General Conference of Seventh-day Adventists, discusses what happens when a person dies and the confusion that the devil has brought regarding this topic. The occult, spiritualism, and satanic influences are on the rise. The worldwide entertainment industry promotes spiritualism.

The devil plans overwhelming delusions at the end of time through mysticism and unbiblical understandings regarding life after death, but we have the privilege of studying the truth straight from God’s Word. Follow this weekly series with Pastor Ted Wilson to counter the devil’s deception with the truth of God.
